<p>See <em><a href="/ucat/colleges-depts/business-administration/#c2">General and Basic Course Requirements</a></em> in the <em>College of Business Administration</em> section for the list of courses needed to meet this requirement.</p>
<h3>Business Core</h3>
<p>See <em><a href="/ucat/colleges-depts/business-administration/#c3">Business Course Requirements</a></em> in the <em>College of Business Administration</em> section for the list of courses needed to meet this requirement.</p>
