<h3>Course Suggestions for Finance Careers</h3>
<p>Students should select courses based upon their interests and career goals. The finance courses listed below suggest which courses are most appropriate for alternative career paths.</p>
<h4>Corporate Finance and Risk Management</h4>
<p>This area provides an introduction to the work of the financial officer of a company focusing on financial statements, financial characteristics, and financial strategies of different types of firms.</p>
